  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0db8\u0db1\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 40\u0da7 \u0dc5\u0d9f\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inflation in Colombo is close to 40 percent in May",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Surface inflation, measured by the annual point change in the Colombo Consumer Price Index, has increased from 29.8% in April 2022 to 39.1% in May 2022.",
        "Accordingly, the annual point inflation of the food category increased from 46.6% in April 2022 to 57.4% in May 2022, and the annual point inflation of the non-food category increased from 22.0% in April 2022 to 30.6% in May 2022."
      ],
